<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Dateless" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Dateless,</orth> termless, eternal: <cit><quote>death's d. night,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 30.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 30, 6</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a d. lively heat, still to endure,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 2.153.6" default="NO" valid="yes">153, 6</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the d. limit of thy dear exile,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 1.3.151" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 3, 151</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a d. bargain,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 5.3.115" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. V, 3, 115</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>